  "body": "### Description\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n*Summary*: \r\nif history in 1-1 chat contains more than 1 day - user avatar is placed under current day messages\r\n![ios1](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/34253877-1c3c9a22-e652-11e7-80b6-0d9529e3c5e4.png)\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nuser avatar in 1-1 chat in the beginning of chat history\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nuser avatar in 1-1 chat in the beginning of current day chat \r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Start 1-1 chat\r\n- Send some messages\r\n- Continue chat tomorrow\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n* Status version: 0.9.11d463\r\n* Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n#### Logs\r\nTF session: https://app.testfairy.com/projects/4803590-status/builds/7336016/sessions/19/?accessToken=A0r1lkWYYEipgAJnwwWCo90AB2U",
